VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)(?:password|secret|api_key|token)\s*=\s*"[^"]{8,}"
WHEN EXPR MISSING:aws_secretsmanager|var\.|data\.
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects hardcoded secrets in Lambda environment variable definitions.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Lambda Environment Variable Contains Secret.
